<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/19 How to speak so that people want to listen; Making a practice speech based on the tips offered (Host: Way)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=158&amp;p=172#p172"><![CDATA[
Dear Members,<br />Please see below Youtube website and share you’re your opinion <br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session I</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">How to speak so that people want to listen</span><br /><br /><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eIho2S0ZahI" class="postlink">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eIho2S0ZahI</a><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Questions:</span><br />1.How to make a powerful speech? Any points need to be addressed?<br />2.What kind of symptom can deter good listening? Do you agree with youtube content? Gossip/judging/negativity/complaining/excusing/lying/dogmatism<br />3.How to improve your audience listening? Do you agree with youtube content? HAIL (honesty, authenticity, Integrity, Love)<br />4.How to make your speaking voice more attractive? Do you agree with youtube content? (use skill like Register/timbre/prosody/pace/pitch/volume)<br />5.Powerful speaking becomes conscious listening as content addressed, mutual understanding is the key to improve communication, do you agree?<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Session II</span><br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Please take turns to make a practice speech based on the tips offered in Youtube </span><br />1.Topic: what benefits you get from attending Royal club? Or any topic you like<br />2.3-5 mins for each speaker<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold">Agenda</span><br />7:00-7:25 Greetings and free talk<br />7:25-7:30 Opening remarks/ Newcomers self-introduction/ Grouping<br />(Session I)<br />7:30 ~ 8:10pm discussion session (40 mins)<br />8:10 ~ 8:25pm summarization (15 mins)<br />8:25 ~ 8:30pm Regrouping<br />(Session II)<br />8:30 ~9:10pm discussion session (40 mins)<br />9:10 ~9:25pm summarization (15 mins)<br />9:25 ~9:30pm Concluding remarks/feedback from newcomers<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold"><span style="color: #0000FF">The meeting place of Thursday:<br />丹堤咖啡寶慶店：台北市延平南路107號2F (上樓右邊第一區塊)<br />捷運資訊： 近台北捷運–西門站 (4號出口步行約2分鐘，康是美隔壁)<br />丹堤低消: NT$80元<br />最自由的全英文會話聚會,前三次不用交會費,加入會員終生會費NT$500，帶著開放與熱情來學英文<br /></span></span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=827">Jason Tang</a> — Fri Apr 13, 2018 9:21 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
